name: The Call Of Extinction EP
description:
The 2nd 5 track record by Running Death released independently on 25.02.2012.

Tracks: 
1. Unleashed
2. Killing For Gods 
3. Call Of Extinction
4. Celebrate Your Aggression
5. Hunting For Heads
(28.5min in total)

Stream the opener Unleashed now at http://youtu.be/wq4yZDtDW84.
Also available on iTunes, Amazon, etc. by the 25.02.2012.
CDs won't be shipped before the 25.02.2012.

Thank you for your support!
